Class MatrixSeries<K extends Comparable<K>>

java.lang.Object
org.jfree.data.general.Series<K>
org.jfree.data.xy.MatrixSeries<K>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
NormalizedMatrixSeries
public class MatrixSeries<K extends Comparable<K>> extends Series<K> implements Serializable
Represents a dense matrix M[i,j] where each Mij item of the matrix has a value (default is 0).
